Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,改換指揮了 知道了嗎
