Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,請好好地品嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:41.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歷多亞 幫了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,顫抖吧 驚懼吧
