Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我加倍奉還給你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,盲目攻擊只會出醜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,坦克已任由我宰割了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要趕上！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不能與你會合了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:19.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了自己死亡的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:30.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,諾裏斯大佐發出了煙霧信號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼顏色的？諾裏斯怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是紅色...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:41.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,無法會合 凱魯格連號起航吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,凱魯格連號起航準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,驅動動力導管 解除開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,分別雖然是件痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可時間已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:08.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS是我一個人的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,距凱魯格連號起航還剩不到20分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:16.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候轉守為攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,沒子彈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是左手被打廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,反射神經倒不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這招你躲得掉嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,漫不經心可是會致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 主回路在哪裏
