Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,手... 快按我說的做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:26.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴... 301呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼要活著回去
