Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,呵 醒過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:11.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我！要活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,與愛娜再次相會！
