Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:25.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長他！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,擺脫了困擾的傻瓜還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,復活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這個聲音...
