Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:43.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜醬要出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:54.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:05.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:32.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然會遇上愛娜小姐思念的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣的人生啊
